  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Our Favourite Restaurants With a View</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13103249/wintergarden-1.jpg" alt="restaurants with a view" data-udi="umb://media/90ea28151cd04056867b2852c9b8ce36" /></p>
<p>After a long day of walking and sightseeing, you deserve a meal that’s as beautiful as the scenery around you. Imagine savouring a delicious meal amidst the breath-taking vistas of Europe, where the feast for your eyes matches that of your palette. </p>
<p>Just picture yourself outside, sipping a refreshing glass of wine, basking in the fresh mountain breeze, and taking in the awe-inspiring view as the sun bids adieu. Pure bliss, right?</p>
<p>Well, lucky for you, our <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Summer Holidays">walking holidays</a> lead you straight to the most jaw-dropping destinations in Europe.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532}" title="Montana Art Deco Hotel">Lakeside Views at Hotel Montana</a></h2>
<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #7ea537;"><img src="/media/13103202/14_hotel-montana-luzern-scala-restaurant-terrace-1.jpg" alt="restaurants with a view" data-udi="umb://media/ae13512d7e6e4e0b85a32f1d2440c606" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/70b1a325037e4112bc5e6feeb41d725f}" title="Lake Lucerne">Lake Lucerne, Switzerland</a></h3>
<p>Prepare to be wowed by the <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/switzerland/lucerne/hotel-montana">Art Deco Hotel Montana</a> in Lucerne - a luxurious oasis perched in a prime spot overlooking Lake Lucerne. It’s a spectacular example of what hotels are all about- a little slice of luxury away from home in an outstanding location with exquisite views.</p>
<p>Echoing the peak of 1920s tourism, this hotel boasts lavish style and charm. Its prime highlight, aside from its excellent location and view, is the Scala Restaurant. </p>
<p>Inspired by tastes from southern Switzerland, Italy, France, and Greece, the menu is carefully created by skilled chefs and changes seasonally to highlight local and seasonal ingredients for innovative dishes. There's also a wide selection of wines for every taste and a great new vegan menu.</p>
<p>And let’s not forget the pièce de résistance, the Scala Terrace. With a panoramic view of Lake Lucerne and its charming town, this is where you’ll want to savour every last bite and sip.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/b7cb20549ac64a2e8c93a319309ed136" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7cb20549ac64a2e8c93a319309ed136}" title="Hotel Sentido Galomar"><span>Cliffside Charm at Hotel Sentido Galomar </span></a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13103232/galomar-atlantis-breakfast_07112018_mg_1530_0063_lowres-1.jpg" alt="restaurants with a view" data-udi="umb://media/d5e050e799f8426ea74220392fd82338" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1}" title="Canico"><span>Caniço, Madeira</span></a></h3>
<p>Step into <a data-udi="umb://document/b7cb20549ac64a2e8c93a319309ed136" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7cb20549ac64a2e8c93a319309ed136}" title="Hotel Sentido Galomar">Sentido Galomar</a>, where you'll get your own slice of paradise perched atop Caniço's dramatic cliffs.  Here, dining is an experience like not other, with panoramic sea views that accompany every dish.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/ff93225be83c4bebb479d16e56e5cc1b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ff93225be83c4bebb479d16e56e5cc1b}" title="Hotel Seerose">Lakeside Dining at Hotel Seerose</a></h2>
<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #7ea537;"><img src="/media/13103228/seerose-fuschl-am-see-dining-room-1.jpg" alt="restaurants with a view" data-udi="umb://media/7a94666514754b7fa2527164cf6fd764" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Fuschl am See, Austria</a></h3>
<p>Expect to be served gourmet bites with a side of stunning scenery. <a data-udi="umb://document/ff93225be83c4bebb479d16e56e5cc1b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ff93225be83c4bebb479d16e56e5cc1b}" title="Hotel Seerose">Hotel Seerose</a>, tucked in a peaceful lakeside spot, boasts postcard-worthy views of the nearby hills and lake. </p>
<p>The hotel’s a-la-carte restaurant serves up delicious dishes made from fresh, regional produce that will tantalise your taste buds.</p>
<p>And to kickstart your day, you can enjoy a traditional Austrian farmers breakfast that will leave you energised and ready to explore the nearby walking trails. But the real cherry on top is the hotel’s lakeside bar and terrace, where you can unwind with a refreshing drink and soak in the stunning views.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/07fec0ae0d27493fbac2ae579230896c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07fec0ae0d27493fbac2ae579230896c}" title="Spa Resort Alpbacherhof">Peak Views at Hotel Alpbacherhof</a></h2>
<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #7ea537;"><img src="/media/13103229/hotel-alpbacherhof-alpbach-panoramic-terrace-1.jpg" alt="restaurants with a view" data-udi="umb://media/51005eebf3664c798e8830cf0cd7129c" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Alpach, Austria</a></h3>
<p>Despite being only a two minutes’ stroll from the centre of Alpbach, you would be forgiven for mistaking this spa resort hotel for a wilderness retreat. Celebrating uninterrupted panoramic mountain views from the back terrace of the stunning Tyrolean landscape, the hotel is immensely proud of its luxurious ¾ board menu, offering a sumptuous feast of contemporary Austrian Tyrolean cuisine in a traditional Alpine bar and restaurant. </p>
<p>Hotel guests are offered three choices of main course in the evening, and an in-house sommelier will advise you on a huge selection of local wines so you can sit back and savour the food and drink as the sun slips beneath the tips of the mountains. </p>
<p>But one of the best things about the <a data-udi="umb://document/07fec0ae0d27493fbac2ae579230896c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07fec0ae0d27493fbac2ae579230896c}" title="Spa Resort Alpbacherhof">Spa Resort Alpbacherhof</a> is its absolutely outstanding spa facilities. Breath-taking, undisturbed panoramic views across the Alpbach mountains and meadows will completely sweep you off your feet.</p>
<p>The outdoor swimming pool is heated all year around, and guests are allowed to wander around the beautiful gardens throughout the summer, discovering shady spots to enjoy with a book and cup of tea.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Castle Height Bites in Lake Bled </a></h2>
<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #7ea537;"><img src="/media/13103230/adobestock_96310065.jpg" alt="restaurants with a view" data-udi="umb://media/9cce065ca0ec4abb8a4da1e179eccbdc" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled, Slovenia</a></h3>
<p>While many people would relish a table overlooking the iconic <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.blejski-grad.si/en/" target="_blank">Lake Bled castle</a>, having a delicious dinner or lunch from inside the castle is even better.</p>
<p>Built in 1011, Bled Castle has been lovingly restored and holds a museum of Slavic history, exploring the tumultuous story that the castle holds over the course of 1,000 years.</p>
<p>With its vantage point from the top of the precarious cliff overlooking Bled, the lake and the mountains beyond, it’s understandable why anyone would want to build their castle in such a beautiful location. Even more understandable why anyone would want to establish a delicious restaurant on the site too!</p>
<p>Rated again and again as an outstanding restaurant with attentive staff, delicious food, and of course that stunning view across Lake Bled and the Julian Alps towards <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/slovenia/bohinj">Bohinj</a>, guests just keep on returning. The perfect location for a special birthday, anniversary, and the castle even lends itself as a wedding venue as well.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Trattoria Loncrino</h2>
<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #7ea537;"><img src="/media/13103231/adobestock_87090613.jpg" alt="restaurants with a view" data-udi="umb://media/f47bbfaf76504bcda928b25aa2efe84f" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Garda, Italy</a></h3>
<p>Situated in an elevated position above <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy/lake-garda/torri-del-benaco">Torri del Benaco</a> on <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy/lake-garda">Lake Garda</a>, this small, family-run and unassuming restaurant is a hidden gem. </p>
<p>An outdoor terrace that overlooks <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy/lake-garda">Lake Garda</a> and towards Pulciano comes to life with lively locals who love their food genuine, hearty, home cooked, and filled with love and made with the finest locally sourced ingredients. Getting to the restaurant is a leisurely stroll into the hills above <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy/lake-garda/torri-del-benaco">Torri del Benaco</a>, and you are rewarded with the food and wine upon your arrival. </p>
<p>The food is no-frills attached down-to-earth Italian goodness, enhanced by the surrounding beauty of<a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy/lake-garda"> Lake Garda</a>. This restaurants great reputation has spread through the word of mouth and no wonder our guests keep and on returning to it year after year.</p>
<p> </p>
